<arggraph id="micro_k001" topic_id="public_broadcasting_fees_on_demand" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Not everyone should be obliged to pay the TV & radio licence.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[Particularly the younger generations are no longer dependent on the programming of public broadcasters.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[US series are preferred over “Tatort”,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[and online magazines are turned to instead of the “Tagesthemen”.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[The TV & radio licence enables economically independent journalism.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[But as long as the licence payers have no say in the distribution of the funds, the fee quite rightly annoys them.]]></edu>
